        <mxCell id="v_p1" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;1. Upload RISC-V ELF to IPFS&lt;br&gt;2. Evaluator loads into zkVM&lt;br&gt;3. Execute: exitCode 0=pass&lt;br&gt;4. Generate Groth16 ZK Proof&lt;br&gt;5. Submit proof on-chain&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;arcSize=8;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
