        <mxCell id="l1f" value="&lt;b&gt;Market Dynamics&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:9px&quot;&gt;Unfair rubrics get fewer&lt;br&gt;bids. Low-rep evaluators&lt;br&gt;get fewer assignments.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Prevents:&lt;/b&gt; unfair criteria&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;arcSize=10;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
